      "title": "Dallas' name suggests Sajith - G.L. Confirms",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Opposition leader Mr. Sajith Premadasa proposed the name of Member of Parliament Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma for the currently vacant position of President and the nomination was given to the ruling party member G.L. Seconded by Mr. Peiris.",
        "Apart from Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe, who is currently acting as the President, Mr. Anura Kumara Dissanayake of the National People's Power has also joined the presidential battle."
      ],
